    "They point to remarkable progress achieved in various aspects of the technology including advanced control strategies, optimization algorithms and energy storage systems integration.",
    "In addition, the analysis also reveals that China, India and Morocco are the most active producers of this kind of research to date, while high quality and significant research impact has been observed in India in particular.",
